<div class="container mt-4">
  <h3 style="text-align: Left;">
    <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/supporticon-black.png"), alt: "community", height: '50px') %>
    Support
  </h3>
</div>


<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <h4> Have an idea but not sure where to start?</h4>
    <p>
      Book a consultation with us below to discuss training - from upskilling user groups to course evaluations.
      The SciLifeLab Training Hub provides support in training co-creation and delivery to ensure knowledge transfer at
      SciLifeLab is engaging, effective, Open and FAIR, and creates sustainable and lasting learning.
    </p>
    <br>
    <br>
    <!-- Cal inline embed code begins -->
