    </div>


    <div class="row">
      <h4> We support the entire training life cycle:</h4>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="special-box d-flex flex-column p-3">
          <div class="p-2 border align-self-start">

            <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/trainingcycle.png"), alt: 'training cycle', width: '100%') %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">
          <div class="support-box text-center d-flex flex-column p-3">
            <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/collaboration.png"), alt: 'icon', height: '40px') %>
            <h5 style="color:black;">
              Sustainable national delivery
            </h5>
            <p style="font-size:15px;">
              We offer assistance with digitizing your current training offering and helping your existing material grow
              to reach life science professionals across Sweden - sustainably.

            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">
          <div class="support-box text-center d-flex flex-column p-3">
            <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/learning.png"), alt: 'icon', height: '40px') %>
            <h5 style="color:black;">
              Training development
            </h5>
            <p style="font-size:15px;">
              We offer support in the entire training life cycle to effectively ensure your team, users, or students
              stay
              competitive with the pace of technology- and data-driven life science.<br>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">
          <div class="support-box text-center d-flex flex-column p-3">
            <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/tools.png"), alt: 'icon', height: '40px') %>
            <h5 style="color:black;">
              Tools & technical support
            </h5>
            <p style="font-size:15px;">
              We can support your access to our suite of educational tools, platforms, and technology for setting up and
              delivering training.<br><br>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <h4>
      Frequently Asked Questions:
    </h4>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">
        <button data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#FAQ1" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">What can I
          get
          support with?
        </button>

        <div id="FAQ1" class="collapse">

          <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p>
              We can help you at any stage of the training life cycle -- in planning,
              designing, developing, delivering and evaluating. We can connect you with resource guides and best
              practices that are suited for your training needs.
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <br>
      <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">
        <button data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#FAQ2" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Can I book a
          consultation call if I am not affiliated with SciLifeLab?
        </button>

        <div id="FAQ2" class="collapse">

          <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p>
              Our consultation calls are open to everyone who aims to serve the Life Science
              community in Sweden with training. If you are in industry, healthcare, or government, or a non-affiliated
              researcher who would like to bring your knowledge to our audience, please feel free to book a
              call!
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <br>
      <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">
        <button data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#FAQ3" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">How much does
          it cost?
        </button>

        <div id="FAQ3" class="collapse">

          <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p>A first consultation call is free! If your project is better suited for
              personalized short or long term support tracks from the Training Hub, we can discuss this with
              you.
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <br>
      <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">
        <button data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#FAQ4" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">What happens
          during a consultation?
        </button>

        <div id="FAQ4" class="collapse">

          <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p>
              Our consultation calls are 50 minutes, and will be with one of the Training Team
              members. You will receive a confirmation notice that your booking has been approved along with a Zoom
              link.
              During the call, we will listen to your ideas and questions, and provide a first step of support in
              connecting
              you with resources. Afterwards, the Team member will report back to the group and decide on a plan of
              action
              if further support is needed!
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <br>
      <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">
        <button data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#FAQ5" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Should I
          bring
          anything to a consultation call?
        </button>

        <div id="FAQ5" class="collapse">
          <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p>
              It helps to maximize our time if you think through what your aim or goal is.
              Questions, ideas, and enthusiasm!
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
